281
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NEXT TIME
– <i>We're gonna find whoever got Ishino</i></font>

282
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>and put them through</i>
<i>suffering worse than hell.</i></font>

283
00:22:42,250 --> 00:22:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the only thing that</i>
